data.description:
Welcome to your dream home in the much sought after Ormond Lakes. This spacious and inviting residence offers incredible value with its generous square footage, on a corner lot, mature landscaping, and a host of fantastic features that make it perfect for your family, including your furry friends.Step into your private outdoor paradise, complete with a sparkling swimming pool and spa. The fenced-in yard provides security and peace of mind for both your family and pets.The huge upstairs bonus room is a blank  canvas offering endless possibilities. The convenience of a downstairs master suite cannot be overstated. Enjoy the luxury of easy access and privacy, with a spacious master bedroom that includes an en-suite bathroom and easy access to an office.  The 2 car garage is oversized. Working from home has never been more comfortable. This home features a dedicated office space with accessibility from the master suite, providing convenience without compromising on productivity.
Calling all chefs and food enthusiasts! The gourmet kitchen is a true masterpiece, boasting modern appliances, ample counter space, and a functional layout. It opens seamlessly to the main living area, making it ideal for entertaining and family gatherings.
The main living area features cathedral ceilings, creating a grand and airy ambiance that's perfect for both everyday living and hosting special occasions.
The corner lot of this property is beautifully adorned with mature landscaping, adding charm and curb appeal. Enjoy the beauty of well-established trees and plants year-round.
This home offers the best of both worlds: a spacious, comfortable, and well-appointed interior combined with a fantastic outdoor space for all your family's needs. Whether you're looking to relax by the pool, enjoy the convenience of a downstairs master suite and office, or explore the possibilities of the upstairs bonus room, this property has it all.
Don't miss your chance to make this wonderful family home your own. Schedule a visit today and discover how this property can fulfill all your family's dreams and needs. Act fast because this opportunity won't last long!
